span.p: Member visits Tribute for initial check-in
TRiBE creates entry in MS SQL
C2 Pro scanner enters armed mode
Member places finger on scanner 3 times
Member presents ID at Front Desk
Staff clicks 'New Account Activation' in TRiBE
Staff scans ID with Duplex Scanner
Staff asks member to login to account on phone
Staff confirms account by verifying phone number
Staff needs to redo TouchID process
Member places finger once more to verify
Member granted entry for first visit
